  "text": "Given the non-linear system of eq. (5), more advanced mathematical tools aimed at studying the observability for non-linear systems may be required, such as the concept of local weak observability introduced in [CITATION_1] . The reader may consider the synthetic overview of the concepts of observability, Lie derivatives and observability rank condition given within a context of relative localization in [CITATION_2] .",
